parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID assigned upon registration is successful. Required for all requests.

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is to ensure the timestamp of the request. Required for all requests.

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated by partner_id, api path, timestamp and additionalSha256 string using HMAC-SHA256 hashing algorithm.

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error reason if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: warning
response_fields.description: Indicate warning details if hit warning. Empty if no warning happened

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking
